-- Yahoo to reject Microsoft bid: source
-- 
-- Sat Feb 9, 2008 2:34pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/02/09/us-yahoo-microsoft-rebuff-idUSN0954974420080209

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Yahoo Inc. is set to reject Microsoft Corp.'s offer, initially worth $44.6 billion, as undervaluing the business, a source familiar with the situation said on Saturday. 

 The Internet media giant is expected to reject Microsoft's offer on Monday, the source said. (Reporting by  Megan Davies ; Editing by  John O'Callaghan )